Comment (general): rich in bioclasts, Ostracods (A); pteropods (D); spicules (P); bryozoa (P); peloids (P); bivalves, rose bengal stained P. obliq and O. univ

Zone name: PT1b - Globorotalia truncatulinoides Partial-range Zone (Gradstein et al., 2012)

Comment (general): rich in Ostracods. Pteropods, fish tooth, bryozoa, peloids, sponge spicules present; pyritised forams, agglu. forams
